  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You learn any 2 Spells of your choice from any Spell List, provided 1 of them is a Cantrip.</p><p>You learn to express your art in a unique manner, granting you the ability to alter how you cast Spells. Choose the manner of your expression: <strong>Visual</strong> or <strong>Auditory</strong>.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Visual:</strong> Through acrobatics, dancing, juggling, painting, drawing, or miming, you can ignore the <strong>Verbal</strong> Components of a Spell you cast, but you must provide a <strong>Somatic</strong> Component instead.</p></li><li><p><strong>Auditory:</strong> Through singing, playing music, poetry, comedy, or storytelling, you can ignore the <strong>Somatic</strong> Components of a Spell you cast, but you must provide a <strong>Verbal</strong> Component instead.</p></li></ul>",
